      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and represents a solid choice for a driver prioritizing utility and mechanical reliability. While the engine and transmission are sound and the car handles well on the road, potential buyers should expect some cosmetic wear, including minor dents on the exterior and visible aging on the interior upholstery. All major systems are functional, though some secondary features may show their age. It is a dependable daily driver that has been priced to reflect its current state and provides honest value for its next owner.",
