      "description": "Calling all project lovers and DIY enthusiasts! This vehicle is the perfect canvas for someone looking to roll up their sleeves and restore a car to its former glory. While it's currently in poor condition and needs significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a fantastic opportunity for a rewarding restoration project at a great price!",
