    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a peerless example of automotive excellence, this vehicle remains in pristine showroom condition, reflecting a standard of preservation rarely encountered on the secondary market. Every surface, from the unblemished exterior finish to the meticulously curated interior, confirms its status as a premier acquisition for the discerning driver. This is an investment-grade opportunity for those who demand uncompromising quality and absolute mechanical integrity.",
