      "description": "Presented in exemplary, showroom-grade condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class. Meticulously maintained and preserved with uncompromising attention to detail, it offers an aesthetic and mechanical profile indistinguishable from its original debut. Every surface and component reflects a standard of care rarely encountered in the pre-owned market. This is a definitive acquisition for the discerning enthusiast who demands absolute excellence.",
      "price": 46500.0,
